<p>I’ve received some questions over time about how I blog. What platform I use, how I manage dependencies, how I achieve certain effects, how I update, how I handle images etc…</p>

<p>I primarily use <a href="https://www.docker.com">Docker</a>, <a href="https://jekyllrb.com">Jekyll</a>, <a href="https://www.mercurial-scm.org">Mercurial</a> and <a href="https://code.visualstudio.com">Visual Studio Code</a>. Click through to see how I use these things together to create what you’re reading now.</p>

